# Logs / runtime data:
# - The dated verifiable artifacts (logs/*.json, logs/*.md, logs/*.txt)
#   ARE tracked; they form the "verifiable usage records" for the
#   Bitget AI Hackathon submission.
# - The live `logs/demo.log` is the running demo bot's stream and is
#   regenerated every run, so we ignore it.
logs/demo.log